# Summary
This documentation details the HubSpot integration with Amplitude, which sends email campaign events from HubSpot to Amplitude for analysis, supporting 10 predefined email events (like EMAIL_SENT, EMAIL_OPEN) with user properties tracking and allowing marketers to analyze campaign performance through funnel charts and cohort creation.

## Keywords
- HubSpot email campaign tracking
- Email event streaming
- Marketing automation analytics
- Email funnel analysis
- EMAIL_SENT, EMAIL_OPEN events
- HubSpot Portal ID
- Email campaign cohorts
- 1-hour API polling interval
- Email subscription status tracking
- Internal HubSpot ID filtering